    "v2": "Let me see my Savior&#39;s face, Let me all His beauties trace; Show those glorious truths to me Which are only known to Thee.",
    "v3": "Holy Ghost, with pow&#39;r divine Cleanse this guilty heart of mine; In Thy mercy pity me, From sin&#39;s bondage set me free.",
    "v4": "Holy Ghost, with joy divine Cheer this saddened heart of mine; Yield a sacred, settled peace, Let it grow and still increase.",
    "v5": "Holy Spirit, all divine, Dwell within this heart of mine; Cast down every idol\\- throne, Reign supreme, and reign alone."
  },
